620
00:54:49,955 --> 00:54:51,289
Ugh.

621
00:54:52,374 --> 00:54:54,584
Screw this. I'm going for a smoke.

622
00:54:54,751 --> 00:54:56,461
No, no, no, it's not safe out there.

623
00:54:56,628 --> 00:55:00,548
