with my family, I can accept that.

630
00:55:27,492 --> 00:55:30,620
You gotta trust me, okay?
We can fight this.

631
00:55:30,787 --> 00:55:33,373
We stick together long enough
for her to have her baby...

632
00:55:33,540 --> 00:55:37,002
